"Yes, well we still intend to find out where our leader is. That's why we
took prisoners, in exchange for information of where the Decepticons from
the Ark may be. Enjoy it thought, because from now on we will show no more
mercy to fallen opponents." He says continuesly walking. He arrives at a
door on the right, with many more down the hall. "Here is my quarters, we
can speak in private in here" he says opening it, and entering.
